name: Framed Crow Print
description:
Printed onto a vintage dictionary page, inked for more aging, then framed into a simple black frame, these spooky Halloween themed prints are sure to delight as part of any home decor this season!

Each comes in a 5x7 black frame with glass.

These are all hand made, one at a time and will all vary. Make great gifts! These are not toys, please use caution when displaying.

Contact me for a shipping quote to your country.
